173
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:51,060
Kemudian saya mesti mencari dia segera.

174
00:11:51,110 --> 00:11:52,110
Tunggu.

175
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:54,360
Jika anda tergesa-gesa keluar sekarang, anda
hanya akan memburukkan keadaan.

176
00:11:55,160 --> 00:11:56,160
Duduklah.

177
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,450
Keluarga Shi dan istana lain

178
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:03,480
