Grandmaster di mana-mana.

179
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:04,870
Jika anda pergi sekarang,

180
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:06,566
anda akan menarik perhatian kepada diri anda sendiri,

181
00:12:06,590 --> 00:12:08,300
